>>>>>>> ### Three in five cases of type 2 diabetes can be prevented or
delayed. So we're working to help you take action.
>>>>>>> We're supporting people across the UK to find out their risk and take
action to reduce it. But this problem is too big to tackle alone, which is why
we're working to make it easier for people to make healthy choices every day.
We're doing this by raising awareness about risk, helping you to take action,
creating a healthier environment and funding ground-breaking research.
>>>>>>> ## Healthier You National Diabetes Prevention Programme
>>>>>>> We are working together with NHS England and Public Health England to
provide Healthier You NHS Diabetes Prevention Programme (NDPP), the first
national programme to help those who are at high risk of type 2 diabetes. The
programme gives participants personalised support to help them achieve a
healthy weight, improve their diet and become more physically active, all
together which have been shown to reduce the risk of developing the condition.
Use our free Know Your Risk tool to find out if you could start the programme
via your local Healthier You provider today. It couldn't be quicker or easier,
and you may be able to start the programme via online sessions if you are
>>>>>>> Since it started, more than 300,000 people have been a part of the
>>>>>>> If you think the programme might be helpful for you or someone you
know, speak to your GP or Health Practitioner or find out more by visiting the
>>>>>>> Find out more about the NHS Diabetes Prevention Programme.
>>>>>>> It’s really important that everyone understands their risk of type 2
>>>>>>> Type 2 diabetes is still widely misunderstood. Many people are not
aware of the causes of type 2 diabetes or their risk of developing it. This is
why it’s so important for people across the UK to find out their risk.
>>>>>>> Our Know Your Risk tool, developed with the University of Leicester,
helps people to find out their risk and what to do to lower it.
>>>>>>> * #### Find out your risk of getting type 2 diabetes
